      • Character

        public Character​(Room location,
                 String name,
                 String description,
                 String dialogue)
        Overloaded constructor, for adding characters that have pre-assigned fields This is used for most NPCs.
        Parameters:
        location - The room in which the character can be found
        name - The character's name
        description - The character's description
        dialogue - What the character says when the player talks to them

      • Character

        public Character​(Room location,
                 String name,
                 String description,
                 String dialogue,
                 String tradeDialogue)
        Overloaded constructor which adds trade dialogue and initializes a trade list. This is used exclusively for NPCs with items to trade.
        Parameters:
        location - The room in which the character can be found
        name - The character's name
        description - The character's description
        dialogue - What the character says when the player talks to them
        tradeDialogue - What they character says when you trade with them
